  "instructions": [
    "heat 2 tablespoons of ghee in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "add the sliced red onions and cook until they are translucent.",
    "add the sliced red bell peppers and cook for 2-3 minutes.",
    "add the sliced red chili peppers and cook for another minute.",
    "add the diced tomatoes, chicken breast, ginger paste, garlic paste, cumin powder, coriander powder, cardamom powder, black pepper, and salt.",
    "stir well and cook for 2-3 minutes.",
    "add the dasima-kombu and stir well.",
    "cook for 10-12 minutes or until the liquid has thickened and the flavors have melded together.",
    "stir in the lemon juice and cook for another minute.",
    "serve hot and garnish with chopped fresh cilantro if desired.",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
